FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our dog walking service
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the dog walking app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app connects dog owners with trusted local dog walkers. Simply create a profile for your dog, schedule a walk, and we'll match you with an available walker in your area.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What safety measures are in place?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: All our dog walkers undergo background checks and are fully insured. We also provide real-time GPS tracking of walks and photo updates for your peace of mind.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How much does the service cost?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Prices vary depending on walk duration and frequency. You can view our pricing in the app, and we offer package deals for regular walks to help you save.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! You can set up daily, weekly, or custom recurring schedules to ensure your furry friend gets regular exercise.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if I need to cancel a walk?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We understand plans change. You can cancel a scheduled walk up to 2 hours before the start time without any cancellation fee. Later cancellations may incur a small fee.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Dog Walking App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the dog walking app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects dog owners with trusted local dog walkers. Simply create a profile for your dog, select your preferred walking times, and book a walker. You'll receive real-time updates and a report after each walk.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Are your dog walkers vetted and insured?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, all our dog walkers undergo a thorough background check and are fully insured. We also provide ongoing training to ensure the highest quality of care for your furry friend.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How much does the service cost?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Our pricing varies based on walk duration and frequency. We offer competitive rates starting from $15 for a 30-minute walk. You can view detailed pricing in the app and even get discounts for booking regular walks.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What if I need to cancel a scheduled walk?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We understand plans can change. You can cancel a scheduled walk up to 2 hours before the start time without any charge. For cancellations within 2 hours of the walk, a small fee may apply. Check our cancellation policy in the app for more details.
